name: Dark Occultism
desc: Discard 1 card; add 1 "Destiny Board" or 1 Level 8 Fiend monster from your Deck or GY to your hand. During your Main Phase, except the turn this card was sent to the GY: You can banish this card from your GY; place any number of "Destiny Board" and/or "Spirit Message" cards with different names from your hand and/or GY on the bottom of the Deck in any order, then draw the same number of cards. You can only use each effect of "Dark Occultism" once per turn.
